WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.417
I ran out of pretending, so the night speaks plainly.

00:00:06.400 --> 00:00:10.733
Neon trembles on the floor like a thought too heavy.

00:00:13.200 --> 00:00:17.617
Every honest thing arrives wearing the sound of rain.

00:00:20.400 --> 00:00:24.567
We are still here, dimly burning, refusing to lie.

